description: The point shapefile shows locations of the critical care hospitals in the lower 48 states compiled from Health Resource and Service Administration (HRSA) of Dept. of HHS, dataset. There are over 8000 records that have name, address, telephone numbers (where listed) and also number of certified and toal hospital beds available at these hospitals.
